snippet.title: World in Conflict Blues Destruction
snippet.description: Who knew listening to the blues could cause such destruction? Check out this World in Conflict video if you'd like to see some of the special abilities you'll be able to use ingame when you gain enough points to use them. http://www.rtscommunity.com/
